---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout>
  <section class="section-about" aria-label="About The Me">
    <div class="section-about__text">
      <h2 class="section-about__h2">About Me</h2>
      <p class="section-about__p">
        Hey there! I'm <span class="section-about__p section-about__p--author">Yefree</span>, 
        a passionate and outgoing front-end software developer with a deep love for programming. 
        With a professional and detail-oriented approach, I strive to create engaging and 
        user-friendly web experiences using cutting-edge technologies.
      </p>
      <p class="section-about__p">
        In terms of my technical abilities, I have a strong foundation as a front-end developer 
        with expertise in JavaScript, React, and other related technologies. I'm constantly expanding 
        my knowledge and staying up-to-date with the latest industry trends and best practices.
      </p>
      <p class="section-about__p">
        I invite you to join me on this exciting adventure, as we embark on a 
        journey of learning, sharing, and discovering the limitless possibilities
        of front-end development.
      </p>
      </p>
    </div>
    <img class="section-about__img" src="/images/hero.PNG" alt="Illustration about the creator of the blog">
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style lang="scss">
  .section-about{
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(25rem, 100%), 1fr));
    margin: 4rem;
    &__text{
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;

    }
    &__h2{
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 1rem + 7vw, 4rem);

    }
    &__p{
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 600;

      &--author{
        color: rgb(0, 183, 255);
      }
    }

    &__img{
      object-fit: contain;
      object-position: center;
      aspect-ratio: 1;
    }

  }

</style>
